    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/5489640eaa7c6d26c382106fbb5c41a0.poster.avif?t=1680858495\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/5489640eaa7c6d26c382106fbb5c41a0.webm?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/5489640eaa7c6d26c382106fbb5c41a0.mp4?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>有史以来最多汁的VR游戏的续作！打造你的刀具和弓箭收藏。在独特的关卡和迷你游戏之间切出一条通关之路。探索充满活力的Fruitasia世界，成为真正的水果忍者大师！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blades &amp; Music</h2>在手工打造的关卡中一路砍劈。伴随着音乐的节奏切开水果，抵御飞行的水果机器，在猛击水果的过程中测试你的反应能力！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/f00797f434771a221699338f438cdc68.poster.avif?t=1680858495\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/f00797f434771a221699338f438cdc68.webm?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/f00797f434771a221699338f438cdc68.mp4?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bows &amp; Arrows</h2>掌握全新的弓箭，从远处射击水果。将水果排成一排达成连击，并打出会心一击，以提高你的分数！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/8953a4c32d8d71788a4bb777c9ee060a.poster.avif?t=1680858495\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/8953a4c32d8d71788a4bb777c9ee060a.webm?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/8953a4c32d8d71788a4bb777c9ee060a.mp4?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapon Collection</h2>通过完成挑战收集独特的道具和弓箭。试试冰冷的冰弓或复古的像素刀！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/53af5f2977bd45273728f4b7dcbbac9f.poster.avif?t=1680858495\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/53af5f2977bd45273728f4b7dcbbac9f.webm?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/53af5f2977bd45273728f4b7dcbbac9f.mp4?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the World</h2>随着你在游戏中的进展，解锁新的区域。探索训练场，欣赏Fruitasia的风景和声音！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/6bdda9b1b6cf7817bc4de794870bd322.poster.avif?t=1680858495\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/6bdda9b1b6cf7817bc4de794870bd322.webm?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/6bdda9b1b6cf7817bc4de794870bd322.mp4?t=1680858495\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discovery</h2>寻找Fruitasia隐藏的秘密，玩一玩迷你游戏，发现互动！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520/extras/622895994de339a742ff5c41ff415304.poster.avif?t=1680858495\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1575520